  "text": "The paper provides in next sections more details on the reliability prediction methodology and, also, illustrates HMMWV sensitivity analysis results. It should be noted that the presented results are based on a \"modified\" HMMWV vehicle model developed based on incomplete, limited published information [CITATION_1] .",
